$LLY
Eli Lilly (NYSE:LLY) announces top-line results from SURPASS-1 monotherapy clinical trial evaluating the efficacy and safety of tirzepatide compared to placebo in adults with type 2 diabetes.Treatment differences for two estimands – efficacy and treatment-regimen – were evaluated for the three tirzepatide doses (5 mg, 10 mg and 15 mg) compared to placebo.Using the efficacy estimand, the highest dose of tirzepatide led to an A1C reduction of 2.07% and reduced body weight by 9.5 kg (11.0%).51.7% of participants in this arm achieved an A1C less than 5.7% – the level seen in non-diabetic people, 87.9% of partticipants achieved A1C <7%.
